#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:2 5c035a75f5c940768f5ef56b934dd37c
msgid "贡献指南"
msgstr "Contribution Guide"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:4 6170cb5933ff4272a3329e95c68c33a6
msgid "我们欢迎对 esp-faq 项目做出贡献，如修复错误，添加文档等。我们通过 `Github Pull Requests <https://help.github.com/en/github/collaborating-with-issues-and-pull-requests/about-pull-requests>`_ 接受贡献。"
msgstr "We welcome contributions to the esp-faq project, such as fixing errors, adding documentation, and more. We accept contributions through `Github Pull Requests <https://help.github.com/en/github/collaborating-with-issues-and-pull-requests/about-pull-requests>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:7 45cab6870c1e4652b2aebed833e042a5
msgid "提交流程"
msgstr "Submission Process"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:9 8d3d3fadd6564b1fae923929a7c05aab
msgid "这一节，是对 ``新增问题`` 和 ``修改问题`` 两个操作的流程简要介绍，流程中涉及的环节具体要求，请点击链接查看。"
msgstr "This section briefly introduces the workflow for the two operations: ``Adding a Question`` and ``Modifying a Question``. For the specific requirements of each step involved in the workflow, please click the corresponding links for details."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:11 cec29bc8fc48492b8c9c811d612239f9
msgid "针对 ``git`` 相关操作不做具体的介绍，可以查看 `Git 相关教程 <https://git-scm.com/book/zh/v2>`_。"
msgstr "This guide does not provide detailed instructions for ``git`` operations. You may refer to the `Git tutorial <https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:14 9efc380684d24cb48f095072b63d08f3
msgid "新增问题"
msgstr "Adding a Question"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:16 ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:26 6058a2b970d74fbd9f9818721133f293 f3b00d13a71a4f10a4654070060c46f7
msgid "在本地 `新建分支`_，遵循 `分支命名规范`_；"
msgstr "`Create a new branch`_ locally and follow the `Branch Naming Rules`_;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:17 6106f98b2f4a400d8ebea0b5bbac9ab8
msgid "在本地或者 web IDE 找到与问题类型对应的 ``*.rst`` 文件，根据模板格式新增问题；"
msgstr "Find the ``*.rst`` file corresponding to the question type locally or in the web IDE, and add the question according to the template format;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:18 ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:28 58d6b4b0dae047c7855e31aa82beb476 6261727175ba485cab65a644253fa94c
msgid "编辑完成后，打开预览界面查看显示结果是否符合预期，可以使用 `本地编译环境`_ 编译文档，并检查生成网页是否满足；"
msgstr "After editing, open the preview page to check whether the display result meets expectations. You can use the `Local Build Environment`_ to build the documentation and check whether the generated web pages meet the requirements;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:19 16c1d4fb12884d769209e46ba6ab570a
msgid "遵循 `提交信息规范`_，推送到 github 后并提交 Pull Requests；"
msgstr "Follow the `Commit Message Rules`_, push to GitHub, and submit a Pull Request;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:20 ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:30 352441db9e0b4a32afc430a36b65f994 a41847a6175c480aa2d03dabe7b6a725
msgid "若满足上述预期，则 `提交合并请求`_；"
msgstr "If the above expectations are met, `Submit a Pull Request`_;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:21 7c064c6a46954a8ca271e460682bfe83
msgid "待文档所有讨论解决并成功提交 PR，即完成新增问题的流程。"
msgstr "After all documentation discussions are resolved and the PR is successfully submitted, the process of adding a question is complete."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:24 95812e4d4bfa4e87ba7a27e474c21eee
msgid "修改问题"
msgstr "Modifying a Question"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:27 1f64f26f1ad749948ffacc1e6e5d3344
msgid "在本地或者 web IDE 找到与问题类型对应的 ``*.rst`` 文件，修改期望修改的问题；"
msgstr "Find the ``*.rst`` file corresponding to the question type locally or in the web IDE, and modify the question as expected;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:29 832436f518e44e80ac3aa268957768bc
msgid "遵循 `提交信息规范`__，推送到 github 后并提交 Pull Requests；"
msgstr "Follow the `Commit Message Rules`__, push to GitHub, and submit a Pull Request;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:31 f04e1a290581444093a9f172a04ce4a7
msgid "待文档所有讨论解决并成功提交 PR，即完成修改的流程。"
msgstr "After all documentation discussions are resolved and the PR is successfully submitted, the modification process is complete."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:34 65ee98a0993b4935881709fc2137359d
msgid "新建分支"
msgstr "Create a New Branch"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:36 41a6a16623dd45abaf50931abeadd640
msgid "新建分支都基于 **主分支** 进行；操作时，请留意当前所在分支是否为你期望合入的分支。"
msgstr "All new branches should be based on the **main branch**. When operating, please make sure that the current branch is the branch you expect to merge into."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:38 6d3dfa02d2064641969dd9c41c95f5c6
msgid "操作示例:"
msgstr "Example:"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:47 f62744fe82054a0dbaacf95a4ef8a21f
msgid "分支命名规范"
msgstr "Branch Naming Rules"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:49 f89f2b8880c54c17ab3a56fbf481144b
msgid "新增问题：``add/artificial-intelligence_{q&a}``，``{q&a}`` 使用文件名的英语简要，例如新增 ``artificial intelligence camera model`` 问题，分支名：``add/artificial-intelligence_camera_model``。"
msgstr "Adding a question: ``add/artificial-intelligence_{q&a}``, where ``{q&a}`` should be a brief English description based on the file name. For example, when adding the ``artificial intelligence camera model`` question, the branch name should be: ``add/artificial-intelligence_camera_model``."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:51 3eecaed42a2b48c4aa717bb230ad13cf
msgid "修改问题：``mod/artificial-intelligence_q&a``，``q&a`` 使用文件名的英语简要，例如修改 ``artificial intelligence camera model`` 问题，分支名：``mod/artificial-intelligence_camera_model``。"
msgstr "Modifying a question: ``mod/artificial-intelligence_q&a``, where ``q&a`` should be a brief English description based on the file name. For example, when modifying the ``artificial intelligence camera model`` question, the branch name should be: ``mod/artificial-intelligence_camera_model``."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:54 20266454cef84ddcb2b04b87d22b80c4
msgid "问题编辑规范"
msgstr "Question Editing Rules"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:56 ac42a56179a84bc4ac4833db39e94d6a
msgid "参考问题模板。"
msgstr "Refer to the question template."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:59 2451cc1b3f72464c84e24f8680613e63
msgid "问题模块示例"
msgstr "Question Module Example"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:73 156360bb769c4bea801bedefc47939b5
msgid "问题图片示例"
msgstr "Question Image Example"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:93 cdff59bcf70c4c7f802bd5652384aa01
msgid "本地编译环境"
msgstr "Local Build Environment"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:95 f2e24c51a75240d6950a7c3d024bcfd5
msgid "测试验证环境使用 ubuntu 或 Debian 系统，配置 python 环境为 ``3.7``。"
msgstr "The test and verification environment uses Ubuntu or Debian, and the Python environment should be ``3.7``."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:96 582a6038ec5a4f8093b792d0d19c190b
msgid "推荐使用 python 虚拟环境，或者 docker 环境。"
msgstr "It is recommended to use a Python virtual environment or a Docker environment."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:134 3764bac69ecd4cea98e2476e63494634
msgid "提交信息规范"
msgstr "Commit Message Rules"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:136 67661765633d44f69514eaa0585e31d0
msgid "在分支上添加提交信息，以说明添加/修改/删除问题功能。每个提交都有一条消息，例如："
msgstr "Add commit messages on the branch to describe the function of adding/modifying/deleting questions. Each commit has a message, for example:"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:145 d641c8ff19dc48b3ae9b7ea779813211
msgid "提交信息的第一行应类似于“问题类别：添加/修复/删除/更改内容”。第一行以提交要更改的文件名的名称开头。例如："
msgstr "The first line of the commit message should be similar to “question category: add/fix/delete/change content”. The first line should start with the name of the file to be changed by the commit. For example:"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:147 00b8db9307a44bec84eedd0ccb81f92e
msgid "``artificial-intelligence: esp-eye support those camera models.``"
msgstr "``artificial-intelligence: esp-eye support those camera models.``"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:149 414a9863fe0a4b9c814ffd0d6f9b473e
msgid "要添加有关该提交的更多详细信息，请将其放在第一行之后的提交消息中。"
msgstr "If you want to add more details about the commit, put them in the commit message after the first line."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:151 c1ba2189ac604333a751d1f2dcdc5f56
msgid "一个好的 git 提交消息讲述了一个为什么发生更改的故事，因此，阅读提交日志的人可以了解项目的开发。编写良好的提交信息现在看来似乎是在浪费时间，但是在将来尝试了解某些原因更改时，这对您和您的同事很有用（对我们的客户也有用）。"
msgstr "A good git commit message tells a story about why the change happened, so that people reading the commit log can understand the development of the project. Writing a good commit message may seem like a waste of time now, but it will be useful to you and your colleagues in the future when trying to understand why certain changes were made. It is also useful to our customers."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:154 fab771c251944b5aba31a5ad7744fe65
msgid "提交合并请求"
msgstr "Submit a Pull Request"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:156 c5233bac28804de49209e35764e2e853
msgid "一旦完成修改就可以对分支进行第一次提交，如果您需要进行更多的更改，请进行更多提交。完成您对该分支的所有提交后，提交合并请求。"
msgstr "Once you have completed the modifications, you can make the first commit to the branch. If you need to make more changes, please make more commits. After completing all commits on the branch, submit a pull request."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:158 0bc4a95c65f34211974369c2d65578ef
msgid "我们使用 github 合并请求功能将分支合并到主分支中，步骤："
msgstr "We use the GitHub pull request function to merge branches into the main branch. Steps:"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:160 0ac37ba7aa8c4cd1b8eb8cf740de17e2
msgid "将您的分支推送到 github 仓库；"
msgstr "Push your branch to the GitHub repository;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:161 7c6f328f0241488aa08af5380624bf4a
msgid "转到 `esp-faq <https://github.com/espressif/esp-faq>`_，然后单击 “New pull request”；"
msgstr "Go to `esp-faq <https://github.com/espressif/esp-faq>`_, and click “New pull request”;"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:162 7f2290aa72214b4eb1b9f6d567614ee3
msgid "选择您刚创建准备合并的分支，然后填写“合并请求”详细信息。"
msgstr "Select the branch you just created and are preparing to merge, then fill in the  \"Pull Request\" details."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/document-contribution.rst:164 fd226ea5220648adbecb5073ca18a4f9
msgid "参考：`IDF贡献代码 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/contribute/index.html>`_。"
msgstr "Reference: `Contribute to IDF <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/contribute/index.html>`_."

